{"tid":2309239,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"控方：藏兩眼罩可推論參與暴動","createTime":"2020-12-02T11:52:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-02T12:54:20.000Z","uid":25558,"like":6,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"93168165577dec236edf1f3fb2132e15669d13ab","tid":2309239,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T11:52:31.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201202/CJDJTTGDXZHBXMURUFG6ON4I3U/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201202%2FCJDJTTGDXZHBXMURUFG6ON4I3U%2F&d=u42ujRIT%2FE%2FeodHrCKN%2BOXd5d2ehbLCfOFFYxDFDkZk%3D&h=c60c9872\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201202%2FCJDJTTGDXZHBXMURUFG6ON4I3U%2F&h=13f1cfbf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201202/CJDJTTGDXZHBXMURUFG6ON4I3U/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n控方：藏兩眼罩可推論參與暴動<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/_mRaji6WSUS5tKDxGhohezijb-w=/5760x3840/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/XYRJHWNDLBAIPAXHRYCN37KOIY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F_mRaji6WSUS5tKDxGhohezijb-w%3D%2F5760x3840%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FXYRJHWNDLBAIPAXHRYCN37KOIY.jpg&h=582769cf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■去年8月31日港島區遊行演變成警民衝突。資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n【8.31暴動案】<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】去年8月31日港島區遊行演變成警民衝突，七名在銅鑼灣被捕人士遭控暴動等罪，控方開審時明言無影片拍到七人參與暴動，昨再要求法官依賴七人被捕時的衣着裝備、非常接近縱火暴動現場，及逃避警方追捕這三點當中任何一點，推論他們參與暴動；又以其中一人為例，指他雖沒逃走或穿黑衣，但身懷兩個眼罩，又留守現場，認為已可推斷表證成立。法官今裁決。<br />\n<br />\n案件昨在區院續審，控方。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n代表鄒的大狀郭憬憲反駁，沒證據指鄒在現場留守，警方僅在他身上找到護目鏡，控方不能僅憑這一點便推斷鄒參與暴動。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n辯方：眾被告無畏罪逃跑<br />\n<br />\n資深大律師潘熙代表首被告及第四被告陳詞稱，控方沒證據指兩人向警方做出挑撥行為，亦沒證據指兩人與其他人士非法集結。兩人被截停位置與控方所指稱的暴動現場相距甚遠，首被告從商場步出不遠便遭截停，第四被告更是步向警方。潘指兩人裝備僅是保護及醫療裝備，連打火機都沒有，認為控方的推斷天馬行空。<br />\n<br />\n其他被告的大狀亦指被告沒有畏罪逃跑，僅帶防衞裝備。控方則指帶防衞裝備更脗合七被告參與暴動。<br />\n<br />\n。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n案件編號：DCCC9/20"},{"pid":"90626efd62de22a766e4ab0bf64a440d7753b9ab","tid":2309239,"uid":84102,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T11:53:38.000Z","msg":"藏陰莖可推論參與強姦"},{"pid":"6c7f137c1d054e2e770c9b92a8b2b5c213716696","tid":2309239,"uid":71462,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T11:54:32.000Z","msg":"藏良心可推論參與暴動"},{"pid":"fbb9358d9a39793eb3f0d0f6d1f9c3929daa1934","tid":2309239,"uid":121546,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T11:55:55.000Z","msg":"一隻眼罩戴係眼到一隻係屎眼到"},{"pid":"a8388b336563b823ffa42d812aa09c8a1094a098","tid":2309239,"uid":30040,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T11:56:23.000Z","msg":"我屋企有眼罩用黎戴住切洋蔥🧅。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a40118020fb3e7e7693010541df246907639fee2","tid":2309239,"uid":34023,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T11:57:17.000Z","msg":"屌你老母都弱撚智"},{"pid":"aa3e00eecaf4d64efb7984842ef821d209d81817","tid":2309239,"uid":159916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T11:58:50.000Z","msg":"控方係人名？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n姓控名方？"},{"pid":"7708903be7342b9880fbb0a26affcc5d7f47fc27","tid":2309239,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a40118020fb3e7e7693010541df246907639fee2","tid":2309239,"uid":34023,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T11:57:17.000Z","msg":"屌你老母都弱撚智"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T11:58:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img 